title: WWE RAW Total Edition
description:
WWE RAW Total Edition

Operating System: Windows 98/ME/XP
CPU: Pentium III, 500Mhz
Minimum Memory: 64MB RAM. 128 MB required if you're on XP.
Graphics Card: Nvidia TNT2 and GeForce 1, 2 &3; ATI Radeon 7000, 7200, 7500, 8500;
Matrox G450 is the minimum recommended for the game.
Sound Card: DirectX compatible sound card
CD-ROM: IDE or SCSI CD-ROM
Input: Keyboard or mouse required. Gamepads and joysticks are supported.
DirectX: DirectX 8
